	<ThingDef ParentName="ShipSpinalTurretBuilding">
		<defName>shipEterniumSpinalBarrelLaser</defName>
		<label>Eternium spinal barrel: laser</label>
		<description>The final segment of a spinal-mount cannon.\n\nShould be placed outside the ship, unless you want a new hole in your hull.\nMust be connected to a pilot/tactical console or AI core via the heat network.\nRequires sufficient stored power and heat capacity to function.\nSomeone enhanced it with Eternium</description>
